        <h2>
            梁漱溟先生论儒佛道的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3443909">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3443909/" class="title-link">佛法大意</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3443909"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/redlunch/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2190291-121.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/redlunch/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">WuFan</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-07-15"
      class="main-meta">2010-07-15 22:03:41</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3443909_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                    小乘佛法讲五蕴皆空，四谛不立，助我们免受痛苦。五蕴有色，受，想，行，识，色大致可以理解为物质，一切皆因之而起，我们因六根不净而生六尘，于是对人生的幻望有所固执。人生迷妄之本在于二执二取，我执和法执，能取与所取，而我执执于八识，在眼耳鼻舌身意之外，还有末那...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3443909/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3443909_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3443909_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
